# Caffeine build + agentic lock (DDR-026 / DDR-027)

## Build contract

- Backend: sibling `src/backend/mops.toml` (`--default-persistent-actors`) + bare `mops install` / `mops build` / `pnpm bindgen`
- Frontend: `rm -rf dist` + `pnpm build`
- Workspace: `include = ["src/**"]` only
- **Forbidden:** `cd ..` for mops; sibling preflight `.mjs`; `scripts/` paths in caffeine.toml

## Agentic workspace (DDR-027)

| Action | Who |
|--------|-----|
| GitHub import | Operator UI only |
| `redeploy_draft` for `ucnbj-nqaaa-aaaab-aajua-cai` | Operator confirms → platform |
| Build / deploy draft | Agent — **build only** |
| Production reinstall | **Never** for draft IC0503 |

## Agents must not

- Claim they imported from GitHub
- “Fix” IC0503 by editing EntitlementMigration or adding entitlementId fields
- Recommend revert to Caffeine “Version 132” as the code fix
- Reinstall production to clear draft IC0503
- Edit locked caffeine/mops files without a new DDR

## If IC0503 on draft

1. Stop source edits
2. Request `redeploy_draft` (draft backend `ucnbj-nqaaa-aaaab-aajua-cai`)
3. Then build only

